social_posts.post_text: Thanks so much for having me @_beyondboards_ 🙏❤️ you can listen to my episode wherever you get your podcasts, as well as the link in my bio
Thank you so much to everyone who made it out in Portland for the party at @cals_pharmacy what an awesome night ❤️🙏 photos by @treblig_
Thanks Amaya, picked from my line drawing book and tattooed @idlehandsf #tattoo #traditionaltattoo

Alright SF, you don’t wanna miss this! Come celebrate with me at the beautiful @dlxskateshop this January! We will have books, drinks, merch, special guests, and more! You’ve been asking for a Bay Area party so now is your chance! I’m stoked to be doing one here in town and can’t wait to see you all there. Please spread the word! Flyer by the absolute best @jeffrassier 🙏❤️
First one of 2023, hoping this brings you some good luck, Danielle! Tattooed at @idlehandsf

So excited to announce a show at the beautiful @thebetancourtgallery in Miami next month! Please join us for a collection of photographs from @_brandonburdine @plasticbath and @easterxdaily showcasing the process behind @letitkillyoubook 📸 We will also be selling books at the show—back to back nights! It’s going to be a blast and this will be a one of a kind event. Thanks so much to my friend @javierbetancourt for setting this up— can’t wait to see you all there ☀️
Hannya for Jay made at @idlehandsf

Huge thank you to everyone who came out to @dlxskateshop to celebrate despite the weather. Meant so much to see you all. Love you San Francisco. Huge thank you to everyone at DLX for all of their support 🖤 photos by @plasticbath
Hannya tattooed at the one and only @idlehandsf for Andres 🤍 #tattoo #idlehandsf #hannya #sanfrancisco
Couple cats @idlehandsf
Healed tiger and fresh rose for Bryce made @idlehandsf

A year of tattooing my friend, Grant. Jobs like this one make me really appreciate tattooing and the friendships it manifests. Tattooed at @idlehandsf #irezumi #japanesetattoo #traditionaltattoo #sanfrancisco
Skull and rose for @wicked.west.nails made at @idlehandsf #tattoo #traditionaltattoo #sanfrancisco
Prove to everyone you’re not a poser and get a skate tat! Thanks @gripgrand tattooed at @idlehandsf

My book Let It Kill You is sold out. What an insane couple of years that I’ll never forget. Thank you so much to everyone who bought a copy, it means so much to me. On to the next thing and you won’t want to miss it. Make sure you’re following @letitkillyouseries to see what’s next 🎥🍿
Tats/other @idlehandsf

My guy @rosskjones and I will be holding down the @idlehandsf booth at the @capcityclassictatcon in a couple weeks! Excited to see all of you soon. I’ll have original paintings, merch, new designs and more 🖤
A panther for Jackie! Picked from my flash and tattooed at @idlehandsf #tattoo #traditionaltattoo #idlehandsf
Couple ladies for, Kevin. Tattooed at @idlehandsf #tattoo #traditionaltattoo #idlehandsf
Saw a healed one at @capcityclassictatcon thanks to everyone who got tattooed, what a fun weekend 🖤 thanks @brittyb916 for the invite
Thanks for filling my cancellation today, Melissa 💐 tattooed at @idlehandsf
Panther @idlehandsf DM or email for appts

Officially in production for LET IT KILL YOU the series. Spent ten days in LA shooting recently and you won’t want to miss these episodes. Please follow @letitkillyouseries for more sneak peaks 🖤 📸 @plasticbath
Snake and skull for extreme sports athlete and friend @k3vinbraun tattooed at @idlehandsf ❤️

I spent a very hot week in Austin, TX with the @rogerskateco and @nocomplyatx crew shooting another episode of @letitkillyouseries with @sieben_up that you can’t miss. Due out soon. Shot by @trevarcushing and 📸 from @plasticbath
Dragon! I’m always booking appts @idlehandsf send an email or DM for a spot 🖤
Heart tat made at @idlehandsf
Painted a couple new sheets for two of my current favorite artists @kevinspankylong and @mike_lottie_ all designs available to be tattooed 📞
Little sheet for @coreyduffel and @adoredskateboarding ❤️
Dragon for my friend @k3vinbraun tattooed at @idlehandsf
These are my designs for the @mercyslc anniversary party tomorrow, please come celebrate a powerhouse tattoo shop with all of us. See you there 🎉
Peony for my friend @scott.warfield.clark who runs @dadsluncheonette which if you haven’t checked out, you’re blowing it. A favorite in the bay for sure 🍴
Another @idlehandsf flash day is coming. Bringing back the gumball machine as well! Bring a friend, come alone, make friends in line— whatever you want. See you soon. Starts at 11AM
💀🦋 @idlehandsf
Panther! Made at @idlehandsf thanks Alex! #tattoo #traditionaltattoo #panthertattoo
So excited to finally be able to share this trailer with you all. First 3 episodes coming very soon 🖤
Picked from my flash and tattooed at @idlehandsf
Some tattoos without color that I made @idlehandsf recently. Want a tattoo? Just send me a DM or email for an appt 🖤

Bay Area! I’m thrilled to invite you all out for an advanced screening of @letitkillyouseries this is a FREE screening! First come, first served. Drinks, popcorn, special guests and more. It’s going to be a great time! Followed up with an after party across the street at @kilowatt_bar_sf with a DJ set from @black__thumb and pizza from @thatsouttasight I’d love to see you all and can’t wait, please spread the word ❤️ flyer by the incredible @niki_rain

Here’s a Thrasher interview with yours truly about the series. Thankful to @sieben_up for my second interview with @thrashermag for Let It Kill You ❤️ link in my bio. See you all tonight at @roxie_theater

A massive thank you to everyone who came out for the first @letitkillyouseries screening at the @roxie_theater 🙏 Thank you to @thrashermag and @shattucks_pics for coming out to take these photos! Huge thank you to @kilowatt_bar_sf and @rickless_life for hosting the after party and to @thatsouttasight for the best pizza in town- such a special night to finish out the year ❤️ here’s a few pics from the night, more on @thrashermag site
Another year of tattoos @idlehandsf thanks to everyone that supports myself and the shop! Looking forward to more in 2024 ❤️

LOS ANGELES! I’ll be doing an advanced screening of @letitkillyouseries at Highland Theater in Highland Park on 1/12! I’d love to see you all there. This is a FREE screening. First come, first served. Can’t wait to see you all soon! Flyer by the best @marina_inoue 🖤

I recently had the privilege of sitting down with @monsterchildren for an interview on my new series @letitkillyouseries link in my bio for the full spread, thanks to @joshsabini for the good time 🖤 see you all Friday night in Los Angeles for a screening 🍿
